<Narrative>
	<section:Section>
		<text:Paragraph>
			The question of machine consciousness has shifted from philosophical
			speculation to engineering concern.
		</text:Paragraph>
	</section:Section>

	<section:Section>
		<text:Paragraph>
			Early work in artificial intelligence sidestepped the consciousness
			question entirely, focusing on behavioral equivalence.
		</text:Paragraph>
	</section:Section>
</Narrative>
